{"tid":1567924,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 極限足球 Extreme Football - 韓國 3 VS 3 即時對戰 3D街頭足球遊戲","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T06:32:01.000Z","uid":66923,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d916a6da95183be83cca114eaea363a7092af5e2","tid":1567924,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rIOkNs0A2D0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FrIOkNs0A2D0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=4180779a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Extreme-Football-916944588656568/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FExtreme-Football-916944588656568%2F&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=b02df1f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Extreme-Football-916944588656568/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MJWlsg7nCXQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMJWlsg7nCXQ&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=cbd0f6e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MJWlsg7nCXQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FrePaJpbxLo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFrePaJpbxLo&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=441e3735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FrePaJpbxLo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲簡介</span></span></strong><br />\nExtreme Football（極限足球）是一款3D真人3 vs 3的街頭足球競技比賽遊戲，精美的遊戲人物設計，全新的遊戲操作體驗，相比傳統足球遊戲偏重的競技性，極限足球擁有更多的角色選擇，並提服裝系統和專屬技能選項，創新的足球玩法等！<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.winudf.com/v2/image1/Y29tLm5pbmVtZ2FtZXMuZm9vdGJhbGxfc2NyZWVuXzBfMTU2NTczNDc2MF8wOTU/screen-0.jpg?h=355&amp;fakeurl=1&amp;type=.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.winudf.com%2Fv2%2Fimage1%2FY29tLm5pbmVtZ2FtZXMuZm9vdGJhbGxfc2NyZWVuXzBfMTU2NTczNDc2MF8wOTU%2Fscreen-0.jpg%3Fh%3D355%26fakeurl%3D1%26type%3D.jpg&h=805db6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲特色</span></span></strong><br />\n- 與好友一起對戰全世界玩家的即時三對三足球比賽！<br />\n- 多人足球遊戲，每場遊戲速度快！<br />\n- 球員解鎖與收集：所有球員都具有固有的個人技術和專有技能！<br />\n- 支持一對一、二對二以及三對三！<br />\n- 在全球或地區範圍內挑戰排名！<br />\n- 可與好友一起創建或加入俱樂部，分享策略、一起對戰！<br />\n- 收集多種球員Skin<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.winudf.com/v2/image1/Y29tLm5pbmVtZ2FtZXMuc29jY2VyX3NjcmVlbl8wXzE1NjcyNjE3OTNfMDM0/screen-0.jpg?fakeurl=1&amp;type=.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.winudf.com%2Fv2%2Fimage1%2FY29tLm5pbmVtZ2FtZXMuc29jY2VyX3NjcmVlbl8wXzE1NjcyNjE3OTNfMDM0%2Fscreen-0.jpg%3Ffakeurl%3D1%26type%3D.jpg&h=99fa22ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲玩法</span></span></strong><br />\n手機上的街頭足球，玩出你的足球free style，享受沒有足球規則的自由足球對戰體驗。<br />\n你可以使用各種不同的技能來配合進球，與另外兩名隊友配合進攻或防守。<br />\n另外遊戲還提供了豐富多樣的對戰模式，讓你能夠享受每個瞬間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.winudf.com/v2/image1/Y29tLm5pbmVtZ2FtZXMuc29jY2VyX3NjcmVlbl82XzE1NjcyNjE4MDRfMDMy/screen-6.jpg?fakeurl=1&amp;type=.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.winudf.com%2Fv2%2Fimage1%2FY29tLm5pbmVtZ2FtZXMuc29jY2VyX3NjcmVlbl82XzE1NjcyNjE4MDRfMDMy%2Fscreen-6.jpg%3Ffakeurl%3D1%26type%3D.jpg&h=a40164f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲畫面</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k46oQ2MhXM8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk46oQ2MhXM8&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=06d31a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k46oQ2MhXM8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://im